+----------+----------+    +----------+----------+    +----------+----------+
           |                        |                        |
           |                        |                        |
           v                        v                        v
  - A/B Testing Guide               - Main site sections     - Information architecture
  - Data-driven insights              (Hero, Intro, PM,      - Text content for all sections
  - Clean, modern UI                  AI-PM, Stats)          - Placeholders for visuals
  - Interactive features            - Navigation & Footers
  - AI integration                  - Semantic HTML

